sources.description:
*Hansel & Gretel* - In this modern retelling of the classic horror tale, teen siblings are enslaved by a psychotic recluse within her house of horrors in the woods.
2013.  Stars: Dee Wallace, Brent Lydic, Jonathan Nation, Stephanie Greco.

*Hansel Vs Gretel* - When Gretel falls under a dark spell and organizes a coven of witches, Hansel must find the courage to fight his twin sister and the sinister forces controlling her.
2015.  Stars: Brent Lydic, Lili Baross, Aqueela Zoll
